trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> class contains a single search reference returned by the server.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference" /> 類別包含伺服器傳回的單一搜尋參考。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference.Controls" /> property contains an array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects returned by the server in the search reference.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference.Controls" /> 屬性包含伺服器在搜尋參考中傳回之 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> 物件的陣列。

trans-unit.source: An array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> objects returned by the server in the search reference.
trans-unit.target: 伺服器在搜尋參考中傳回之 <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.DirectoryControl" /> 物件的陣列。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference.Reference" /> property contains an array of <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> objects returned by the server in the search reference.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="P:System.DirectoryServices.Protocols.SearchResultReference.Reference" /> 屬性包含伺服器在搜尋參考中傳回之 <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> 物件的陣列。

trans-unit.source: An array of <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> objects returned by the server in the search reference.
trans-unit.target: 伺服器在搜尋參考中傳回之 <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> 物件的陣列。
